SELECT
Customers.CustomerID,
Customers.FirstName,
Customers.LastName,
SUM(Orders.TotalAmount) AS TotalPurchaseAmount
FROM
`chatwithdata-451800.RetailDataset.Customers` AS Customers
JOIN
`chatwithdata-451800.RetailDataset.Orders` AS Orders
ON
Customers.CustomerID = Orders.CustomerID
GROUP BY
Customers.CustomerID,
Customers.FirstName,
Customers.LastName
ORDER BY
TotalPurchaseAmount DESC
LIMIT 5
